summary: skips the betheseda logo at the start of skyrim
descriptionHtml:
Replaces the 6 or so second long Betheseda logo with a 7milisecond long symbol of skyrim in 1080p

=installation=
extract to your skyrim root folder (commonly in C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Steam\\steamapps\\common\\skyrim)

if asked to merge folders click yes.

If asked to replace, click yes
